// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0311 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 4a315cc1-fdd2-5bfb-bc28-c06cb3ea35bd

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *azure linux:3.0* OR ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
